OL,5,Ccompany
OL,7,F'As deaf people we are part of
OL,8,Fsociety' - Granada's Zoe Muldoon went
OL,9,Fto meet Claire to hear what changes
OL,10,Fshe'd like to see.
OL,12,FA deaf woman from Stockport says she
OL,13,Fhas been 'blatantly discriminated
OL,14,Fagainst' after her energy company
OL,15,Frefused to speak to her through an
OL,16,Finterpreter.
OL,18,FClaire Cummings uses video call relay
OL,19,Fservices - which instantly connect her
OL,20,Fto a British Sign Language interpreter.
