OL,3,CA deaf woman says she's been
OL,4,C'discriminated against' by her energy
OL,5,Ccompany
OL,7,FThe service, called CONVO, allows
OL,8,FClaire to make calls to the likes of
OL,9,Futility companies and banks.
OL,11,FShe said it's usually a
OL,12,Fstraightforward process - but when she
OL,13,Fneeded to make an emergency call to
OL,14,FScottish Power - it was anything but
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,FThat's despite the energy company's
OL,18,Fown website stating it offers video
OL,19,Frelay service calls for BSL signers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
