OL,3,CA deaf woman says she's been
OL,4,C'discriminated against' by her energy
OL,5,Ccompany
OL,7,FClaire said: "The company refused to
OL,8,Ftake the call and asked what CONVO
OL,9,Fwas. So I explained the law, I
OL,10,Fexplained about accessibility, and
OL,11,Fthey completely refused the call. So I
OL,12,Fasked to speak to a manager, and again
OL,13,Fthey refused."
OL,15,FScottish Power has since apologised,
OL,16,Fbut Claire says more training is
OL,17,Fneeded for staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
