OL,3,CA deaf woman says she's been
OL,4,C'discriminated against' by her energy
OL,5,Ccompany
OL,7,F"This was a really urgent issue, I
OL,8,Fneeded to sort things out and they
OL,9,Fstopped me calling. It just felt
OL,10,Fextremely frustrating and worrying and
OL,11,Fdistressing."
OL,13,FClaire is the chair of Manchester Deaf
OL,14,FCentre and helped create the
OL,15,FManchester BSL festival.
