OL,3,CA deaf woman says she's been
OL,4,C'discriminated against' by her energy
OL,5,Ccompany
OL,7,F"It's really important we should
OL,8,Finclude everybody in society.
OL,9,FEverybody has something to contribute
OL,10,Fand as deaf people we are part of
OL,11,Fsociety. We can make a contribution -
OL,12,Fwe have ideas and knowledge and
OL,13,Funderstanding."
OL,15,FA spokesperson told us they were very
OL,16,Fsorry for the issues Claire faced.
