OL,3,CA deaf woman says she's been
OL,4,C'discriminated against' by her energy
OL,5,Ccompany
OL,7,FThey said: "we are dedicated to
OL,8,Fproviding accessible service options
OL,9,Ffor all of our customers and have a
OL,10,Fthird-party service to provide trained
OL,11,Fstaff who can conduct customer calls
OL,12,Fthrough a BSL interpreter."
OL,14,F"Regrettably, on this occasion Ms
OL,15,FCummings did not receive this service
OL,16,Fand the customer service she did
OL,17,Freceive was far below what we strive
OL,18,Fto deliver."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
